https://github.com/infomecanoexpress-dev/mecanoexpress-website
Étape 2 : Créer le premier fichier (package.json)
Cliquez sur "creating a new file" (lien bleu sur la page)
Dans le champ "Name your file", tapez : package.json
Copiez-collez ce contenu :
{
  "name": "mecanoexpress-website",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next dev",
    "build": "next build",
    "start": "next start",
    "lint": "next lint"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "14.2.3",
    "react": "^18",
    "react-dom": "^18",
    "mongodb": "^6.3.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.19",
    "postcss": "^8.4.38",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.4.3"
  }
}
